g direct to airline websites nine times out of 10 - but don't be afraid to check those out as well - the more you research the better prepared you'll be.\nGo where others aren't\n\"You could save hundreds of pounds per person by flying somewhere else,\" Nicky said.\nTraditionally popular Christmas getaway locations include Lapland (for obvious reasons), Paris, Vienna, New York, London and Reykjav\u00edk - so consider avoiding those if you aren't dead set on a destination.\n\"No matter where you're based, you can find good deals by heading to off-season locales and setting your sights somewhere far from where most people tend to flock.\"\nAlbufeira, Portugal, is the most affordable short haul sun destination, with St Paul's Bay, Malta and Paphos in Cyprus also good options, according to loveholidays.\nMeanwhile, Dubai offers the lowest prices for those looking to go long haul, the site's data indicates.\nDon't be afraid to use points\nNicky's final tip is to consider using any rewards scheme or points you can lay your hands on.\nMobile phone providers, broadband, insurance, bank accounts and more all allow you access to a number of travel schemes that may require you to opt-in or have been secretly ticking away in the background.\n\"Using the full range of your rewards can help you put your points and miles to great use,\" Nicky said.\nCheck what you have access to and don't be afraid to use any points you may have built up!", "url": "https://news.sky.com/story/cost-of-living-latest-mars-reduces-size-of-popular-galaxy-chocolate-bar-12615118", "image": "https://e3.365dm.com/23/09/1600x900/skynews-christmas-dinner-turkey_6298826.jpg?20230926143315", "publishedAt": "2023-09-26T14:22:00Z", "source": {"name": "Sky News", "url": "https://news.sky.com"}}, {"title": "INSIGHT-India's BJP, the world's biggest party, plots election drive of epic scale", "description": "Kolkata North, where and his group are campaigning, is a prime example of an early priority seat being targete